document.title: The Beowulf Thesaurus Linked Data Annotation
document.intro: The Beowulf Thesaurus is a set of Linked Data annotations that reference the IRIs of A Thesaurus of Old English (https://oldenglishthesaurus.arts.gla.ac.uk/). The dataset can be browsed as a textual thesaurus within the web application Evoke and is available via http://evoke.ullet.net/c... -
